author: jleroux
msg: The Sales by Store Report was wrong has it did not use a complex alias for quantityOrdered (OrderItem.quantity - OrderItem.cancelQuantity) but only OrderItem.quantity. Thus canceled quantities were not taken into account.
A little drawback is that if there are 0 values sold this values show. But actually it's not a problem since it informs the user that all quantities ordered for this product has been canceled
